Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.50,0:26:56.05,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HF7C34B&}有點任性也不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.57,0:26:59.75,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HF7C34B&}你會原諒我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.17,0:27:03.50,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HF7C34B&}總覺得你好像變得有點
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.56,0:27:07.17,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HF7C34B&}會讓我想說出「討厭」的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.44,0:27:10.68,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HF7C34B&}你說我一邊苦笑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:14.31,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HF7C34B&}一邊露出困擾的表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.64,0:27:21.74,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HF7C34B&}儘管如此 也沒有任何事 是我辦不到的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.96,0:27:25.22,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H1A99F1&\t(0,1000,\3c&H1A99F1&)\t(1770,1000,\3c&HEA9455&)}我想變得 更加完美
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.39,0:27:29.19,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}一掃那些感傷的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.28,0:27:36.74,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&HA335ED&\t(0,1480,\3c&HA335ED&)\t(1540,1000,\3c&H13D21B&)\t(3340,1000,\3c&H5EA2FD&)}也想變得更強 只為了守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.45,0:27:40.75,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}我懂你 但你懂我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.06,0:27:45.66,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}無時無刻 都期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.03,0:27:52.55,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}能將你那溫柔的微笑獨自佔有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.82,0:27:55.30,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}吶 所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.55,0:28:00.50,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}想跟我來談場戀愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.58,0:28:05.23,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}好想一直 在離你最近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.58,0:28:10.76,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\3c&H5EA2FD&}監視著我最喜歡的你